topic.title: How would a cracker cash out credit cards?
topic.body:
I was wondering if there was a safe way,as a homie has some card numbers.Buying cryptocurrencies usually require to upload an ID before,ordering stuff online to your home is also not the greatest idea.
The data have already been stolen,so if not me,someone else is gonna cash 'em out.Then I might as well do it :D

1588013341_13Pvy84dV1dMFAjrmAp7c8Aibs3uo.body:
@nekololi: the average price for a card on dark web markets is somewhere between 10-20$.
Whereas cashing out just even one can get you 100x that amount.I don't wanna waste them..

Yeah,this cracka still has to learn :DDD
Can you link some?I used to know some from deepdotweb,but since it has been shut down,I can't seem to find any viable
So anyone with a link please?
